  <description>
    <p>
      Launcher is a modern application launcher for Linux built with GTK4
      and libadwaita.
    </p>
    <p>
      It provides instant search for installed applications, a built-in
      calculator, and an extensible architecture for adding custom features.
      Launcher integrates seamlessly with modern Linux desktop environments.
    </p>
  </description>

